metadata.name: Guardians of the Icaros
metadata.description:
Remember to breathe, as the vibrations of the Icaros begin to rearrange the vibrating patterns of Nature. Clarity is coming soon. 


The reality matrix is composed of wave forms; everything else is but a persistent illusion. The Icaros are sacred amazonian chants, that have been passed down over millenia. These magical incantations imprint divine patterns into the frequencies that define your life. However, before these divine energies can perform their magick, you must first pass the guardians of the gateway. 


This NFT will serve to bring forth clarity of mind, body and spirit, by providing a visual reminder that this life is but a dream. The path of the shaman is free of obstacles, aside from those which you place in your own way. This NFT is here to remind you that it's up to you, how your story will unfold. The Guardians of the Icaros await you.
